see <- import("p_see_dep_update.dta") %>% 
  mutate(weak = str_detect(app_udep_rc2, "|||||||||||||||||||||||"),
         top_uni = str_detect(app_udep_rc2, "|||||||||||"),
         public = str_detect(app_udep_rc2, "|"))

see_2 <- see %>% 
  filter(weak == 0) %>%
  select(-weak) %>%
  filter(!(dep_id %in% c(138, 1011, 1260, 1732, 2346, 2367, 3135, 3142, 3577, 3703)))
see_2 %>% 
  group_by(cyr) %>%
  summarize(avg_see = mean(see),
            sd_see = sd(see), 
            n= n()) %>%
  mutate(cyr = cyr - 1911) %>%
  ggplot(aes(cyr, avg_see)) +
  geom_point() +
  geom_line() +
  theme_bw() +
  theme(panel.grid.major.y = element_line(), 
        text = element_text(size = 40), 
        axis.title = element_text(size = 40)) +
  scale_x_continuous(limits = c(100, 110), breaks = c(100, 102, 104, 106, 108, 110)) +
  scale_y_continuous(limits = c(40, 70)) +
  scale_color_stata() +
  labs(x = "", y = " (%)")

see_2 %>%
  mutate(uni_typ = case_when(top_uni == 1 ~ 0,
                             top_uni == 0 & public == 1 ~ 1,
                             top_uni == 0 & public == 0 ~ 2)) %>%
  mutate(uni_typ = factor(uni_typ, labels = c("", "", ""))) %>%
  group_by(cyr, uni_typ) %>%
  rename( = uni_typ) %>%
  summarize(avg_see = mean(see),
            sd_see = sd(see),
            n = n()) %>%
  mutate(cyr = cyr - 1911) %>%
  ggplot(aes(cyr, avg_see, color = )) +
  geom_point() +
  geom_line() +
  theme_bw() +
  theme(panel.grid.major.y = element_line(), 
        text = element_text(size = 40), 
        axis.title = element_text(size = 40), 
        axis.title.x = element_text(vjust = 0.2),
        axis.title.y = element_text(vjust = 1),
        axis.text = element_text(size = 40),
        legend.text = element_text(size = 40),
        legend.title = element_blank(),
        legend.position = "bottom",
        legend.box.spacing = unit(0.0005, "npc")) +
  scale_x_continuous(limits = c(100, 110), breaks = c(100, 102, 104, 106, 108, 110)) +
  scale_y_continuous(limits = c(40, 70)) +
  #scale_colour_brewer(palette = "Set1", name = "") +
  scale_color_stata() +
  labs(x = "", y = " (%)")

see_filled <- import("p_see_filled.csv") %>% 
  mutate(app_udep_rc2 = str_replace_all(app_udep_rc2, 
                                        c("" = "(", "" = ")"))) %>%
  rename(latest_moecd_scd2_filled = latest_moecd_scd2)

#export(see_filled, "p_see_filled.dta")

see_filled <- see_filled %>% 
  mutate(b_fd = str_sub(latest_moecd_scd2_filled, 6, 7),
         n_fd = str_sub(latest_moecd_scd2_filled, 6, 8),
         d_fd = str_sub(latest_moecd_scd2_filled, 6, 9),
         STEM = if_else(n_fd %in% c("051", "052", "053", "054", "061", "071", "072", "073"), 1, 0)) %>%
  mutate(STEM = factor(-STEM, labels = c("STEM", "non-STEM")))
see_filled %>%
  group_by(cyr, STEM) %>%
  summarize(avg_see = mean(see),
            sd_see = sd(see),
            n = n()) %>%
  mutate(cyr = cyr - 1911) %>%
  ggplot(aes(cyr, avg_see, color = STEM)) +
  geom_point() +
  geom_line() +
  theme_bw() +
  theme(panel.grid.major.y = element_line(), 
        text = element_text(size = 40), 
        axis.title = element_text(size = 40),
        axis.title.x = element_text(vjust = -0.2),
        axis.title.y = element_text(vjust = 1),
        axis.text = element_text(size = 40),
        legend.text = element_text(size = 40),
        legend.title = element_blank(),
        legend.position = "bottom",
        legend.box.spacing = unit(0.005, "npc")) +
  scale_x_continuous(limits = c(100, 110), breaks = c(100, 102, 104, 106, 108, 110)) +
  scale_y_continuous(limits = c(40, 70)) +
  scale_color_stata() +
  labs(x = "", y = " (%)")

see_nfd <- see_filled %>%
  group_by(cyr, n_fd) %>%
  summarize(avg_see = mean(see),
            sd_see = sd(see),
            n = n(),
            b_fd = first(b_fd)) %>%
  ungroup() %>%
  mutate(cyr = cyr - 1911,
          = factor(as.numeric(b_fd), labels = c("", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "")),
          = factor(as.numeric(n_fd), labels = c("", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "")),
         nfd_class = case_when( %in% c("", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "") ~ 1,
                                %in% c("", "", "", "", "", "", "", "") ~ 2,
                                %in% c("", "", "", "", "") ~ 3,
                                %in% c("", "", "") ~ 4))
## `summarise()` has grouped output by 'cyr'. You can override using the `.groups`
## argument.
  ggplot(see_nfd, aes(cyr, avg_see, color = , alpha = nfd_class)) +
  geom_point(size = 0.8) +
  geom_line() +
  theme_bw() +
  theme(panel.grid.major.y = element_line(), 
        text = element_text(size = 22.5),
        axis.title.x = element_text(size = 40, vjust = -0.05),
        axis.title.y = element_text(size = 40),
        axis.text.x = element_text(size = 20),
        axis.text.y = element_text(size = 30),
        legend.spacing.x = unit(0.2, "cm"),
        legend.spacing.y = unit(0.2, "cm"),
        legend.key.size = unit(0.01, "npc"),
        legend.text = element_text(size = 22.5),
        legend.position = "bottom",
        legend.box.margin = margin(r = 2, l = 0, unit = "pt"),
        legend.box.spacing = unit(0.003, "npc"),
        strip.text.x = element_text(size = 20)) +
  guides(color = guide_legend(ncol = 9, byrow = TRUE)) +
  scale_x_continuous(limits = c(100, 110), breaks = c(101, 104, 107, 110)) +
  scale_y_continuous(limits = c(25, 90), breaks = c(30, 50, 70, 90)) +
  labs(x = "", y = " (%)") +
  facet_wrap(~, nrow = 2) +
  scale_alpha_continuous(range = c(0.7, 1), guide = "none")
